UR  - https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/0304407685901599
AB  - A stochastic coefficient regression model is applied to a cross-section of data supplied by individual commercial banks to derive estimates of the sources of funds diverted to MMDA deposits and their effect on the monetary aggregates. An algorithm for the restricted least squares estimation of the covariance matrix of the coefficients is derived.
